## File Type Guidelines

### Markdown Files (`.md`)
- **Language**: English
- **Purpose**: Documentation, guides, notes
- **Exception**: None - always English

### TypeScript/JavaScript Files (`.ts`, `.tsx`, `.js`, `.jsx`)
- **Comments**: English
- **Code**: English (variable names, functions, etc.)
- **User-facing strings**: Vietnamese (if displayed to users)
- **Technical strings**: English (error codes, etc.)

### Prisma Schema Files (`.prisma`)
- **Comments**: English
- **Model/Field names**: English
- **Enum values**: English (technical identifiers)

### MDX Files (`.mdx`)
- **Documentation MDX**: English
